# pepeline-rs
Fast rust-python librarian for internal needs of an organization
```py
from pepeline import screentone, fast_color_level, read, save
img = read(<"img path">, 0, 0)
img = fast_color_level(
    img,     
    in_low = 10,
    in_high = 240,
    out_low = 0,
    out_high = 255,
    gamma = 1.0
)
img = screenton(img, dot_size=7)
save(img, "out.png")
```
